    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208820/extras/7e12c29ede264757a4aef81bec939d9d.avif?t=1768256443\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Compete in this galactic test of skill with your own customizable <strong>Grabitoon!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208820/extras/765c6d7bb69037c1c44f9a20df755f9e.poster.avif?t=1768256443\" width=598 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208820/extras/765c6d7bb69037c1c44f9a20df755f9e.webm?t=1768256443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208820/extras/765c6d7bb69037c1c44f9a20df755f9e.mp4?t=1768256443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Get ready to rumble!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208820/extras/98e954832839da365d6c4c8bef766dd6.poster.avif?t=1768256443\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208820/extras/98e954832839da365d6c4c8bef766dd6.webm?t=1768256443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208820/extras/98e954832839da365d6c4c8bef766dd6.mp4?t=1768256443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>An Experience for Everyone! </strong><br> <br>Bring your friends and smack 'em over the head in this physics-based party game <strong>for up to four players</strong>! <br><br>From kids to grandpas, <strong>Grabitoons!</strong> is <strong>a game everybody</strong> can enjoy. Easy to pick up with a streamlined control scheme, and <strong>accessible for all!</strong> <br><br>Play with your partner in <strong>1 vs 1 scenarios</strong>, pit your kids amongst each other, or <strong>gather the whole family </strong>for an all-out <strong>Grabitoons!</strong> experience!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208820/extras/7e559c0de0ec1105458c84a8f65c7d0c.poster.avif?t=1768256443\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208820/extras/7e559c0de0ec1105458c84a8f65c7d0c.webm?t=1768256443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208820/extras/7e559c0de0ec1105458c84a8f65c7d0c.mp4?t=1768256443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Grab, throw, smack and wack your way through more than <strong>15 different mini-games</strong>, conquer the different variants and <strong>unlock new pieces</strong> to build your own <strong>Grabitoon!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208820/extras/496d3b3e3699bcfb8f6ee008964c6ccf.avif?t=1768256443\" width=600 height=400 /></span>",
